{"tid":1639823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[尋車cam]夜晚10點半左右大埔警署附近有細佬懷疑比黑警圍毆","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T00:48:12.000Z","uid":41411,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"22cb42a8c383513b41e9455e6e8920a7957354fb","tid":1639823,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:47:44.000Z","msg":"轉載自FaceBook:<br />\n<br />\n時間：約10:30<br />\n地點：大埔警署迴旋處附近行人路<br />\n<br />\n頭先我行到警署附近，見到有個細佬訓低咗，當時有堆人圍住佢，佢全身麻痺，活動唔到，跟住我即刻去睇下有無野可以幫手。<br />\n<br />\n個細佬喊住，好驚咁講番事發經過。當時夜晚十點半左右，佢係警署出面見到有架旅遊巴，而佢就拎部手機出黎影低，點知俾班警察喝住，但係因為細佬戴住airpod﹐唔知道原來警察喝緊佢，跟住成班警察突然從後勒住佢條頸，㩒佢落地，圍毆佢。之後仲用武力捉住細佬手指開電話鎖，仲恐嚇佢講出屋企地址，之後成班警察返番入警署。<br />\n<br />\n我地班街坊有人安慰細佬，有人call細路父母，有人call救護，有人check附近車有無車cam。之後救護車黎到，救護員問緊細路傷勢既時候，兩部警車加一班警察又突然係警署衝出黎，即刻問我地發生咩事，又大聲兇我地叫我地走，又話我地係咪有人係現場目擊事發經過或者拍片影相，又串我地咁多人無理由無影到片。細佬一見到警察，情緒即刻好衝動，係咁話好驚，叫警察快d走，救護即刻抬佢上車，希望佢冷靜到，可以呼吸順暢番。跟住，我地班街坊係咁叫警察走，班警察鬧番我地，話我地唔好再集結，有咩就番警署講，再唔係就去投訴。之後，任啟邦議員黎到，了解發生乜事。細佬最後送去那打素醫院。<br />\n<br />\n而加唯一希望有車cam拍低事發經過，因為當時係警署附近，人流好少，細佬話當時見到好似有個中年男人經過，但係就算見到又如何呢...求主保守細佬康復及佢一家平安🙏🏿😔(補充：當時細佬係無戴口罩，只係影咗一張相，已經俾人圍)<br />\n<br />\n呼籲：如果有人十點半左右係警署對出迴旋處揸車經過，試下check下車cam﹐睇下有無錄低事發經過。同埋，希望任啟邦議員繼續跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n有冇人果段時間揸車或者路經大埔警署又見到發生咩事！！！急要片/相！"},{"pid":"2468eefa9022d6c7ce9e02eb56f6de3a806835a5","tid":1639823,"uid":283686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d6cab3b24fb3b5e348b2d49ae05b2b7d3f9368","tid":1639823,"uid":324247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45c68b15d1376b5add3b065459f175efb5d5819","tid":1639823,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f6e36fa44e4a6a353c5216773baab5627cedcd","tid":1639823,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d859fce9819376af875764294e715be43ed88624","tid":1639823,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:19:21.000Z","msg":"黑社會正仆街"},{"pid":"f2f893416933b16a69dc270a14dd605261e25f84","tid":1639823,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:21:06.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"c717be36a0f9d0e8dd80de01d3c5c5e1e03340be","tid":1639823,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3966d835047a7dae5c24fda899ed5c691209285","tid":1639823,"uid":176947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:53:00.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"8d53f0fd4c238b626c054ab5f54ebf8f3523651a","tid":1639823,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:17:58.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"1d132d353f40537df0ca59f4c229ec18a1a4c293","tid":1639823,"uid":37451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50065700b77ae2b5fc3d7361373dafa889e84c14","tid":1639823,"uid":112421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:24:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c592cf2cd37e947a971145b59a26e8a69d7416d","tid":1639823,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"推！恐怖分子成班周圍走，夜晚真係唔好自己一個出街！"},{"pid":"bef35dbb655e32edc05223bfdb74a02d83a671ab","tid":1639823,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"8bcb40b827cbad2ab210b96785773b8f9776df73","tid":1639823,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a002e742253bfc8ce79eb7fe2fdc299c3af6913","tid":1639823,"uid":85146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99429bbeac4e485de86338326830fd7a9b804db4","tid":1639823,"uid":259945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"港共/黑警<br />\n一直以為年青人<br />\n沒有正常腦袋<br />\n同真係會驚到<br />\n唔識反抗"},{"pid":"c460259dcc5677d996e9a32c6dd89925e793db97","tid":1639823,"uid":255690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:32:32.000Z","msg":"海量文宣比你airdrop Print出黎同放上Twitter FB IG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1597128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1597128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7e79a1adc507d9bb7635162ffe3863464bdca8b","tid":1639823,"uid":21262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a1c2d9158fafee50d14e42ce0244459b7562c4","tid":1639823,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:41:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫<br />\nHong Kong Police brutality database</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=80357f9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版